A quick hack I wrote a few years back.  For example, I sort my .newsrc
file thus:

alias sortn '( fgrep : ~/.newsrc | sort ; fgrep -v : ~/.newsrc | sort ) | hold ~/.newsrc'

Runs on 4.2. Some mods may be needed for other systems.

